{"tid":1956906,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"獨媒：蘭桂坊酒店隔離人士確診 住客詢問患者房間樓層遭拒","createTime":"2020-04-03T13:34:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T13:39:30.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bceb321b02875add5e27ce5c11ed6ba626878ad4","tid":1956906,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:34:36.000Z","msg":"（獨媒特約報導）位於上環九如坊的蘭桂坊酒店週五（4月3日）以書面通知住客，指有住客確診武漢肺炎，並已經送院。酒店在信中強調，外判專業清潔公司已對患者的房間以及周圍徹底清潔和消毒；正在酒店內接受隔離的獨媒記者因感到不安，致電前台查詢患者居住樓層和房間號碼，惟在兩度追問下均遭職員拒絕回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1072148\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1072148&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BrV8WQSydv6El4C3YWjT4Eg%3D&h=c2b0f74a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1072148&h=82e46584\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1072148</a>"},{"pid":"5ca8d21e18fcb701b0b01232a9ab79a267e3a309","tid":1956906,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:39:30.000Z","msg":"走啦仲問，離開座building呀"}]}